text: The latest MacBook Air and MacBook Pro are powered by Apple’s M1 chip, which runs cooler and therefore doesn’t need a fan as often as older models. @JoannaStern puts the new models through a series of tests to see how quiet they really are. #WSJWhatsNow https://t.co/kc97F0fhTK https://t.co/ygmcM3QX89
